steps.description:
In the **Permissions** tab, edit the **Bucket policy** and paste this JSON (replace `YOUR-BUCKET-NAME`):
```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [{
    "Sid": "PublicReadGetObject",
    "Effect": "Allow",
    "Principal": "*",
    "Action": "s3:GetObject",
    "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::YOUR-BUCKET-NAME/*"
  }]
}
```

Once connected, open a query window and run a test command:
```sql
CREATE DATABASE testdb;
USE testdb;
CREATE TABLE users (id INT, name VARCHAR(50));
SELECT * FROM users;
```
